{"tid":1416332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再講樽頸 而家咁樣係最好","createTime":"2019-08-05T14:54:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T15:00:49.000Z","uid":37610,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c0b565eefb6b2ae35027dcc74abe40441b4873ca","tid":1416332,"uid":37610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:54:08.000Z","msg":"今日真係好熱 多謝有手足俾退熱貼 感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先 請各位起一起我底 睇下我之前個Po <br />\n我好欣慰 公務員出黎集會 甚至罷工<br />\n<br />\n點解係最好 <br />\n因為 依家最有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">張力</span></span>既時候 你拉我推 互不相讓<br />\n<br />\n係一場<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">拔河</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家一定要堅持團結 keep 住團火 <br />\n<br />\n不過有少少建議 <br />\n我都會講返我之前D Post <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">投訴之刀</span></span> 將投訴信放滿政府各部門 特別狗屋 <br />\n依把刀 係非常有用 亦係專屬我地香港人<br />\n<br />\n至於泛民代表民間開記者會太行 <br />\n應該每一個團體 每一個人 最好每日都要拍片回應該日的行動 俾新聞媒體 報導 <br />\n<br />\n勇武 就算核彈都唔好割蓆 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不捉鬼 不割蓆 不分化 不被捕 <br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最後再講講 只要大家用下腦 轉個彎 就可聚焦 <br />\n<br />\n發夢扔垃圾去 狗舍 貼下 你老豆亂打人 再扔 <br />\n等等"},{"pid":"b32966c1ffef526760d5d4803e62be25f8d24836","tid":1416332,"uid":37610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:54:23.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"3c6c4cc21d9dd18a656cfad763ba0ea3886c981d","tid":1416332,"uid":37610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:54:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"faa79e24707bede765f7fb9aa1cda55e08173628","tid":1416332,"uid":37610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:54:50.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"878f691b266caf4d60609d3e06073543f8521fa4","tid":1416332,"uid":37610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:55:06.000Z","m